<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4645885>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Toumeyella crataegi Kondo and González on Crataegus mexicana. A. Twig of C. mexicana infested with T. crataegi. Inset showing several adult females tightly clustered on twig. B. An aggregation of T. crataegi, with numerous adult females. Reddish brown nymphs can be seen near the base to the left of the twig (San Nicolás Zecalacoayan, Puebla, Mexico). Photos: Jorge Valdez-Carrasco." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4645885/files/figure.png" .

